    LEFT JOIN (

) AS [t4] ON [t2].[Id1] = [t4].[ContentPageId]

    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CreaDate], [f].[CreaUser], [f].[DeletedDate], [f].[Desc], [f].[FormCode], [f].[IsActive], [f].[LangId], [f].[Mail], [f].[MailCC], [f].[ModDate], [f].[ModUser], [f].[Name], [f].[OrderNo]
        FROM [FormType] AS [f]
        WHERE [f].[DeletedDate] IS NULL
    ) AS [t] ON [c].[FormTypeId] = [t].[Id]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [c0].[Id], [c0].[Address], [c0].[BannerButtonText], [c0].[BannerText], [c0].[ButtonLink], [c0].[ButtonText], [c0].[ButtonTitle], [c0].[ContentData], [c0].[ContentOrderNo], [c0].[ContentShort], [c0].[ContentTypes], [c0].[CreaDate], [c0].[CreaUser], [c0].[DeletedDate], [c0].[Description], [c0].[ExternalLink], [c0].[FormTypeId], [c0].[IsActive], [c0].[IsClick], [c0].[IsFooterMenu], [c0].[IsForm], [c0].[IsHamburgerMenu], [c0].[IsHeaderMenu], [c0].[IsPublish], [c0].[IsSideMenu], [c0].[IsSubMenu], [c0].[LangId], [c0].[Link], [c0].[Location], [c0].[LocationLink], [c0].[MetaDescription], [c0].[MetaKeyword], [c0].[MetaTitle], [c0].[ModDate], [c0].[ModUser], [c0].[Name], [c0].[OrderNo], [c0].[OrjId], [c0].[ParentId], [c0].[TagManager], [c0].[TemplateType], [c0].[VideoLink]
        FROM [ContentPage] AS [c0]
        WHERE [c0].[DeletedDate] IS NULL
    ) AS [t0] ON [c].[ParentId] = [t0].[Id]

) AS [t4] ON [t2].[Id1] = [t4].[ContentPageId]

        SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CreaDate], [f].[CreaUser], [f].[DeletedDate], [f].[Desc], [f].[FormCode], [f].[IsActive], [f].[LangId], [f].[Mail], [f].[MailCC], [f].[ModDate], [f].[ModUser], [f].[Name], [f].[OrderNo]
        FROM [FormType] AS [f]
        WHERE [f].[DeletedDate] IS NULL

    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [c0].[Id], [c0].[Address], [c0].[BannerButtonText], [c0].[BannerText], [c0].[ButtonLink], [c0].[ButtonText], [c0].[ButtonTitle], [c0].[ContentData], [c0].[ContentOrderNo], [c0].[ContentShort], [c0].[ContentTypes], [c0].[CreaDate], [c0].[CreaUser], [c0].[DeletedDate], [c0].[Description], [c0].[ExternalLink], [c0].[FormTypeId], [c0].[IsActive], [c0].[IsClick], [c0].[IsFooterMenu], [c0].[IsForm], [c0].[IsHamburgerMenu], [c0].[IsHeaderMenu], [c0].[IsPublish], [c0].[IsSideMenu], [c0].[IsSubMenu], [c0].[LangId], [c0].[Link], [c0].[Location], [c0].[LocationLink], [c0].[MetaDescription], [c0].[MetaKeyword], [c0].[MetaTitle], [c0].[ModDate], [c0].[ModUser], [c0].[Name], [c0].[OrderNo], [c0].[OrjId], [c0].[ParentId], [c0].[TagManager], [c0].[TemplateType], [c0].[VideoLink]
        FROM [ContentPage] AS [c0]
        WHERE [c0].[DeletedDate] IS NULL
    ) AS [t0] ON [c].[ParentId] = [t0].[Id]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [c1].[Id], [c1].[Address], [c1].[BannerButtonText], [c1].[BannerText], [c1].[ButtonLink], [c1].[ButtonText], [c1].[ButtonTitle], [c1].[ContentData], [c1].[ContentOrderNo], [c1].[ContentShort], [c1].[ContentTypes], [c1].[CreaDate], [c1].[CreaUser], [c1].[DeletedDate], [c1].[Description], [c1].[ExternalLink], [c1].[FormTypeId], [c1].[IsActive], [c1].[IsClick], [c1].[IsFooterMenu], [c1].[IsForm], [c1].[IsHamburgerMenu], [c1].[IsHeaderMenu], [c1].[IsPublish], [c1].[IsSideMenu], [c1].[IsSubMenu], [c1].[LangId], [c1].[Link], [c1].[Location], [c1].[LocationLink], [c1].[MetaDescription], [c1].[MetaKeyword], [c1].[MetaTitle], [c1].[ModDate], [c1].[ModUser], [c1].[Name], [c1].[OrderNo], [c1].[OrjId], [c1].[ParentId], [c1].[TagManager], [c1].[TemplateType], [c1].[VideoLink]
        FROM [ContentPage] AS [c1]
        WHERE [c1].[DeletedDate] IS NULL

    WHERE [c].[DeletedDate] IS NULL AND [c].[LangId] = @__langId_Value_0 AND [c].[Link] = @__request_Link_1
) AS [t2]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[ContentPageId], [d].[CreaDate], [d].[CreaUser], [d].[DeletedDate], [d].[DocType], [d].[FormsId], [d].[ImageUrl], [d].[IsActive], [d].[IsDesktop], [d].[IsMobile], [d].[LangId], [d].[ModDate], [d].[ModUser], [d].[OrderNo]

    WHERE [d].[DeletedDate] IS NULL
) AS [t3] ON [t2].[Id] = [t3].[ContentPageId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d0].[Id], [d0].[ContentPageId], [d0].[CreaDate], [d0].[CreaUser], [d0].[DeletedDate], [d0].[DocType], [d0].[FormsId], [d0].[ImageUrl], [d0].[IsActive], [d0].[IsDesktop], [d0].[IsMobile], [d0].[LangId], [d0].[ModDate], [d0].[ModUser], [d0].[OrderNo]

    WHERE [d0].[DeletedDate] IS NULL
) AS [t4] ON [t2].[Id1] = [t4].[ContentPageId]

    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CreaDate], [f].[CreaUser], [f].[DeletedDate], [f].[Desc], [f].[FormCode], [f].[IsActive], [f].[LangId], [f].[Mail], [f].[MailCC], [f].[ModDate], [f].[ModUser], [f].[Name], [f].[OrderNo]

        WHERE [f].[DeletedDate] IS NULL
    ) AS [t] ON [c].[FormTypeId] = [t].[Id]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [c0].[Id], [c0].[Address], [c0].[BannerButtonText], [c0].[BannerText], [c0].[ButtonLink], [c0].[ButtonText], [c0].[ButtonTitle], [c0].[ContentData], [c0].[ContentOrderNo], [c0].[ContentShort], [c0].[ContentTypes], [c0].[CreaDate], [c0].[CreaUser], [c0].[DeletedDate], [c0].[Description], [c0].[ExternalLink], [c0].[FormTypeId], [c0].[IsActive], [c0].[IsClick], [c0].[IsFooterMenu], [c0].[IsForm], [c0].[IsHamburgerMenu], [c0].[IsHeaderMenu], [c0].[IsPublish], [c0].[IsSideMenu], [c0].[IsSubMenu], [c0].[LangId], [c0].[Link], [c0].[Location], [c0].[LocationLink], [c0].[MetaDescription], [c0].[MetaKeyword], [c0].[MetaTitle], [c0].[ModDate], [c0].[ModUser], [c0].[Name], [c0].[OrderNo], [c0].[OrjId], [c0].[ParentId], [c0].[TagManager], [c0].[TemplateType], [c0].[VideoLink]
        FROM [ContentPage] AS [c0]
        WHERE [c0].[DeletedDate] IS NULL
    ) AS [t0] ON [c].[ParentId] = [t0].[Id]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [c1].[Id], [c1].[Address], [c1].[BannerButtonText], [c1].[BannerText], [c1].[ButtonLink], [c1].[ButtonText], [c1].[ButtonTitle], [c1].[ContentData], [c1].[ContentOrderNo], [c1].[ContentShort], [c1].[ContentTypes], [c1].[CreaDate], [c1].[CreaUser], [c1].[DeletedDate], [c1].[Description], [c1].[ExternalLink], [c1].[FormTypeId], [c1].[IsActive], [c1].[IsClick], [c1].[IsFooterMenu], [c1].[IsForm], [c1].[IsHamburgerMenu], [c1].[IsHeaderMenu], [c1].[IsPublish], [c1].[IsSideMenu], [c1].[IsSubMenu], [c1].[LangId], [c1].[Link], [c1].[Location], [c1].[LocationLink], [c1].[MetaDescription], [c1].[MetaKeyword], [c1].[MetaTitle], [c1].[ModDate], [c1].[ModUser], [c1].[Name], [c1].[OrderNo], [c1].[OrjId], [c1].[ParentId], [c1].[TagManager], [c1].[TemplateType], [c1].[VideoLink]
        FROM [ContentPage] AS [c1]
        WHERE [c1].[DeletedDate] IS NULL

    WHERE [c].[DeletedDate] IS NULL AND [c].[LangId] = @__langId_Value_0 AND [c].[Link] = @__request_Link_1
) AS [t2]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[ContentPageId], [d].[CreaDate], [d].[CreaUser], [d].[DeletedDate], [d].[DocType], [d].[FormsId], [d].[ImageUrl], [d].[IsActive], [d].[IsDesktop], [d].[IsMobile], [d].[LangId], [d].[ModDate], [d].[ModUser], [d].[OrderNo]
    FROM [Documents] AS [d]
    WHERE [d].[DeletedDate] IS NULL
) AS [t3] ON [t2].[Id] = [t3].[ContentPageId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d0].[Id], [d0].[ContentPageId], [d0].[CreaDate], [d0].[CreaUser], [d0].[DeletedDate], [d0].[DocType], [d0].[FormsId], [d0].[ImageUrl], [d0].[IsActive], [d0].[IsDesktop], [d0].[IsMobile], [d0].[LangId], [d0].[ModDate], [d0].[ModUser], [d0].[OrderNo]

    WHERE [d0].[DeletedDate] IS NULL
) AS [t4] ON [t2].[Id1] = [t4].[ContentPageId]
ORDER BY [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t2].[Id1], [t2].[Id2], [t3].[Id]

    FROM [ContentPage] AS [c]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CreaDate], [f].[CreaUser], [f].[DeletedDate], [f].[Desc], [f].[FormCode], [f].[IsActive], [f].[LangId], [f].[Mail], [f].[MailCC], [f].[ModDate], [f].[ModUser], [f].[Name], [f].[OrderNo]
        FROM [FormType] AS [f]
        WHERE [f].[DeletedDate] IS NULL
    ) AS [t] ON [c].[FormTypeId] = [t].[Id]
    LEFT JOIN (

    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[ContentPageId], [d].[CreaDate], [d].[CreaUser], [d].[DeletedDate], [d].[DocType], [d].[FormsId], [d].[ImageUrl], [d].[IsActive], [d].[IsDesktop], [d].[IsMobile], [d].[LangId], [d].[ModDate], [d].[ModUser], [d].[OrderNo]

) AS [t4] ON [t2].[Id1] = [t4].[ContentPageId]

    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CreaDate], [f].[CreaUser], [f].[DeletedDate], [f].[Desc], [f].[FormCode], [f].[IsActive], [f].[LangId], [f].[Mail], [f].[MailCC], [f].[ModDate], [f].[ModUser], [f].[Name], [f].[OrderNo]
        FROM [FormType] AS [f]
        WHERE [f].[DeletedDate] IS NULL
    ) AS [t] ON [c].[FormTypeId] = [t].[Id]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [c0].[Id], [c0].[Address], [c0].[BannerButtonText], [c0].[BannerText], [c0].[ButtonLink], [c0].[ButtonText], [c0].[ButtonTitle], [c0].[ContentData], [c0].[ContentOrderNo], [c0].[ContentShort], [c0].[ContentTypes], [c0].[CreaDate], [c0].[CreaUser], [c0].[DeletedDate], [c0].[Description], [c0].[ExternalLink], [c0].[FormTypeId], [c0].[IsActive], [c0].[IsClick], [c0].[IsFooterMenu], [c0].[IsForm], [c0].[IsHamburgerMenu], [c0].[IsHeaderMenu], [c0].[IsPublish], [c0].[IsSideMenu], [c0].[IsSubMenu], [c0].[LangId], [c0].[Link], [c0].[Location], [c0].[LocationLink], [c0].[MetaDescription], [c0].[MetaKeyword], [c0].[MetaTitle], [c0].[ModDate], [c0].[ModUser], [c0].[Name], [c0].[OrderNo], [c0].[OrjId], [c0].[ParentId], [c0].[TagManager], [c0].[TemplateType], [c0].[VideoLink]
        FROM [ContentPage] AS [c0]
        WHERE [c0].[DeletedDate] IS NULL
    ) AS [t0] ON [c].[ParentId] = [t0].[Id]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [c1].[Id], [c1].[Address], [c1].[BannerButtonText], [c1].[BannerText], [c1].[ButtonLink], [c1].[ButtonText], [c1].[ButtonTitle], [c1].[ContentData], [c1].[ContentOrderNo], [c1].[ContentShort], [c1].[ContentTypes], [c1].[CreaDate], [c1].[CreaUser], [c1].[DeletedDate], [c1].[Description], [c1].[ExternalLink], [c1].[FormTypeId], [c1].[IsActive], [c1].[IsClick], [c1].[IsFooterMenu], [c1].[IsForm], [c1].[IsHamburgerMenu], [c1].[IsHeaderMenu], [c1].[IsPublish], [c1].[IsSideMenu], [c1].[IsSubMenu], [c1].[LangId], [c1].[Link], [c1].[Location], [c1].[LocationLink], [c1].[MetaDescription], [c1].[MetaKeyword], [c1].[MetaTitle], [c1].[ModDate], [c1].[ModUser], [c1].[Name], [c1].[OrderNo], [c1].[OrjId], [c1].[ParentId], [c1].[TagManager], [c1].[TemplateType], [c1].[VideoLink]
        FROM [ContentPage] AS [c1]
        WHERE [c1].[DeletedDate] IS NULL
    ) AS [t1] ON [c].[OrjId] = [t1].[Id]
    WHERE [c].[DeletedDate] IS NULL AND [c].[Link] = @__request_Link_0
) AS [t2]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[ContentPageId], [d].[CreaDate], [d].[CreaUser], [d].[DeletedDate], [d].[DocType], [d].[FormsId], [d].[ImageUrl], [d].[IsActive], [d].[IsDesktop], [d].[IsMobile], [d].[LangId], [d].[ModDate], [d].[ModUser], [d].[OrderNo]
    FROM [Documents] AS [d]
    WHERE [d].[DeletedDate] IS NULL
) AS [t3] ON [t2].[Id] = [t3].[ContentPageId]

[MetaKeyword1], [t1].[MetaTitle] AS [MetaTitle1], [t1].[ModDate] AS [ModDate2], [t1].[ModUser] AS [ModUser2], [t1].[Name] AS [Name2], [t1].[OrderNo] AS [OrderNo2], [t1].[OrjId] AS [OrjId1], [t1].[ParentId] AS [ParentId1], [t1].[TagManager] AS [TagManager1], [t1].[TemplateType] AS [TemplateType1], [t1].[VideoLink] AS [VideoLink1]
    FROM [ContentPage] AS [c]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CreaDate], [f].[CreaUser], [f].[DeletedDate], [f].[Desc], [f].[FormCode], [f].[IsActive], [f].[LangId], [f].[Mail], [f].[MailCC], [f].[ModDate], [f].[ModUser], [f].[Name], [f].[OrderNo]
        FROM [FormType] AS [f]
        WHERE [f].[DeletedDate] IS NULL
    ) AS [t] ON [c].[FormTypeId] = [t].[Id]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [c0].[Id], [c0].[Address], [c0].[BannerButtonText], [c0].[BannerText], [c0].[ButtonLink], [c0].[ButtonText], [c0].[ButtonTitle], [c0].[ContentData], [c0].[ContentOrderNo], [c0].[ContentShort], [c0].[ContentTypes], [c0].[CreaDate], [c0].[CreaUser], [c0].[DeletedDate], [c0].[Description], [c0].[ExternalLink], [c0].[FormTypeId], [c0].[IsActive], [c0].[IsClick], [c0].[IsFooterMenu], [c0].[IsForm], [c0].[IsHamburgerMenu], [c0].[IsHeaderMenu], [c0].[IsPublish], [c0].[IsSideMenu], [c0].[IsSubMenu], [c0].[LangId], [c0].[Link], [c0].[Location], [c0].[LocationLink], [c0].[MetaDescription], [c0].[MetaKeyword], [c0].[MetaTitle], [c0].[ModDate], [c0].[ModUser], [c0].[Name], [c0].[OrderNo], [c0].[OrjId], [c0].[ParentId], [c0].[TagManager], [c0].[TemplateType], [c0].[VideoLink]
        FROM [ContentPage] AS [c0]
        WHERE [c0].[DeletedDate] IS NULL
    ) AS [t0] ON [c].[ParentId] = [t0].[Id]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [c1].[Id], [c1].[Address], [c1].[BannerButtonText], [c1].[BannerText], [c1].[ButtonLink], [c1].[ButtonText], [c1].[ButtonTitle], [c1].[ContentData], [c1].[ContentOrderNo], [c1].[ContentShort], [c1].[ContentTypes], [c1].[CreaDate], [c1].[CreaUser], [c1].[DeletedDate], [c1].[Description], [c1].[ExternalLink], [c1].[FormTypeId], [c1].[IsActive], [c1].[IsClick], [c1].[IsFooterMenu], [c1].[IsForm], [c1].[IsHamburgerMenu], [c1].[IsHeaderMenu], [c1].[IsPublish], [c1].[IsSideMenu], [c1].[IsSubMenu], [c1].[LangId], [c1].[Link], [c1].[Location], [c1].[LocationLink], [c1].[MetaDescription], [c1].[MetaKeyword], [c1].[MetaTitle], [c1].[ModDate], [c1].[ModUser], [c1].[Name], [c1].[OrderNo], [c1].[OrjId], [c1].[ParentId], [c1].[TagManager], [c1].[TemplateType], [c1].[VideoLink]
        FROM [ContentPage] AS [c1]
        WHERE [c1].[DeletedDate] IS NULL
    ) AS [t1] ON [c].[OrjId] = [t1].[Id]
    WHERE [c].[DeletedDate] IS NULL AND [c].[Link] = @__request_Link_0
) AS [t2]
LEFT JOIN (

        SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CreaDate], [f].[CreaUser], [f].[DeletedDate], [f].[Desc], [f].[FormCode], [f].[IsActive], [f].[LangId], [f].[Mail], [f].[MailCC], [f].[ModDate], [f].[ModUser], [f].[Name], [f].[OrderNo]

        WHERE [f].[DeletedDate] IS NULL
    ) AS [t] ON [c].[FormTypeId] = [t].[Id]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [c0].[Id], [c0].[Address], [c0].[BannerButtonText], [c0].[BannerText], [c0].[ButtonLink], [c0].[ButtonText], [c0].[ButtonTitle], [c0].[ContentData], [c0].[ContentOrderNo], [c0].[ContentShort], [c0].[ContentTypes], [c0].[CreaDate], [c0].[CreaUser], [c0].[DeletedDate], [c0].[Description], [c0].[ExternalLink], [c0].[FormTypeId], [c0].[IsActive], [c0].[IsClick], [c0].[IsFooterMenu], [c0].[IsForm], [c0].[IsHamburgerMenu], [c0].[IsHeaderMenu], [c0].[IsPublish], [c0].[IsSideMenu], [c0].[IsSubMenu], [c0].[LangId], [c0].[Link], [c0].[Location], [c0].[LocationLink], [c0].[MetaDescription], [c0].[MetaKeyword], [c0].[MetaTitle], [c0].[ModDate], [c0].[ModUser], [c0].[Name], [c0].[OrderNo], [c0].[OrjId], [c0].[ParentId], [c0].[TagManager], [c0].[TemplateType], [c0].[VideoLink]
        FROM [ContentPage] AS [c0]
        WHERE [c0].[DeletedDate] IS NULL
    ) AS [t0] ON [c].[ParentId] = [t0].[Id]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [c1].[Id], [c1].[Address], [c1].[BannerButtonText], [c1].[BannerText], [c1].[ButtonLink], [c1].[ButtonText], [c1].[ButtonTitle], [c1].[ContentData], [c1].[ContentOrderNo], [c1].[ContentShort], [c1].[ContentTypes], [c1].[CreaDate], [c1].[CreaUser], [c1].[DeletedDate], [c1].[Description], [c1].[ExternalLink], [c1].[FormTypeId], [c1].[IsActive], [c1].[IsClick], [c1].[IsFooterMenu], [c1].[IsForm], [c1].[IsHamburgerMenu], [c1].[IsHeaderMenu], [c1].[IsPublish], [c1].[IsSideMenu], [c1].[IsSubMenu], [c1].[LangId], [c1].[Link], [c1].[Location], [c1].[LocationLink], [c1].[MetaDescription], [c1].[MetaKeyword], [c1].[MetaTitle], [c1].[ModDate], [c1].[ModUser], [c1].[Name], [c1].[OrderNo], [c1].[OrjId], [c1].[ParentId], [c1].[TagManager], [c1].[TemplateType], [c1].[VideoLink]
        FROM [ContentPage] AS [c1]
        WHERE [c1].[DeletedDate] IS NULL
    ) AS [t1] ON [c].[OrjId] = [t1].[Id]
    WHERE [c].[DeletedDate] IS NULL AND [c].[Link] = @__request_Link_0
) AS [t2]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[ContentPageId], [d].[CreaDate], [d].[CreaUser], [d].[DeletedDate], [d].[DocType], [d].[FormsId], [d].[ImageUrl], [d].[IsActive], [d].[IsDesktop], [d].[IsMobile], [d].[LangId], [d].[ModDate], [d].[ModUser], [d].[OrderNo]
    FROM [Documents] AS [d]
    WHERE [d].[DeletedDate] IS NULL
) AS [t3] ON [t2].[Id] = [t3].[ContentPageId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d0].[Id], [d0].[ContentPageId], [d0].[CreaDate], [d0].[CreaUser], [d0].[DeletedDate], [d0].[DocType], [d0].[FormsId], [d0].[ImageUrl], [d0].[IsActive], [d0].[IsDesktop], [d0].[IsMobile], [d0].[LangId], [d0].[ModDate], [d0].[ModUser], [d0].[OrderNo]
    FROM [Documents] AS [d0]
    WHERE [d0].[DeletedDate] IS NULL
) AS [t4] ON [t2].[Id1] = [t4].[ContentPageId]

) AS [t2]
LEFT JOIN (
